Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.29,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.45,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:58.00,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:05.01,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.15,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:22.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:27.23,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:34.17,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.43,0:01:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you rolled a double!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardly what you'd expect from a beginner, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even {\i1}I{\i0} should be able to score a strike or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Put some spirit into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,1... 2... 3... 4... 5... 6!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice gutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's my score at now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... in six frames so far, you're up to 19 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,68 points, and she just rolled a double!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Turkey! What a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Greetings, my dear brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My true brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're well into summer break now, although the heat has let up a bit, at least for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How have things been going for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father was talking about you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you really going to study abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll really be going to Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To tell you the truth, it came as a bit of a shock to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've only just learned that I really do have a brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and now you are about to be going off somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Certainly, that's a big deal to me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...there's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...there's also the matter regarding Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really, at the moment, that's what is troubling me more than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,38. Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Henmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Don't hang up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something I want to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's nothing that I want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to come meet me. I'm over by the station right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the coffee shop, so come meet me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't come. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait for you, no matter how long it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I think I'd like to go to Germany someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your dream, Takehiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I keep at my current studies, then someday, I'll go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that if I go there, I'll find out whether I'm really cut out for this or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Takehiko-san, it sounds like your dream will soon be within reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become the real thing. The real-thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...like my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go, talking about your father again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great, pursuing your dream so devotedly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... what {\i1}is{\i0} it, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, for the moment anyway, I'm really into basketball...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe... I think that a person's dream should be something really worthwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go there, maybe I ought to come along, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go ride the carousel again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaoru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's young...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering how young she is, I must say that this is unusually bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It spreads more quickly when they're so young...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How many years does she have?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The surgery should be sufficient, at least for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The real problem is the possibility of metastasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years. If it hasn't come back within five years, then she should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If she has five years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If she has five years, then she has a future before her, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Takehiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...I might not be able... to go to Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.15,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Only because you're that kind of person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, three days maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the sort who might just wait here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's official. I'm going to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess your dream has come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, live your dream. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream is to go there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Find someone with whom you can share your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That is {\i1}my{\i0} dream now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse the interruption, milady, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...might you know where Takashi-sama is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a telephone call for Takashi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is not in his room, then he is most likely out in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... it's all right, I'll go myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, you have a telephone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right in the middle of something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but could you handle it, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you there? I'm taking the call in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah... er, hello... this is Henmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, I guess Takashi isn't there right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No... no, he's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He has his hands full at the moment, so I am taking the call in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't anything important anyway; I'll just call back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...that time, at Rei's funeral service...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...you helped my brother to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wished to thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was nothing. Really, I felt pretty helpless myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Henmi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:10:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! This is pretty unusual, getting a call from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're drunk, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about her, isn't it. It's not working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to hide it from me. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep trying, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, you'll find a way to get her to come with you to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At any rate, I'm going to head over there now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The usual place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's okay. I'm about to leave anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why you called me in the first place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. I'll be there in fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi-san is going to Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,With Orihara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That, I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't take care of it soon, I won't have time to finish it before the new term starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be free tomorrow, though, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you deliver this to Takehiko for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the documents that Takehiko needs for his foreign study program in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd mail them, but I think he probably wants them as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you write those for him, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he asked me if I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Whenever you have some free time tomorrow would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, it's too late to go tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But he wants them as soon as possible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,T-take a taxi, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course I wanted to get these documents to you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and see that smile of yours again, as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I've been thinking quite a bit about you and Kaoru-no-Kimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How will it all work out when you go to study abroad in Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think that I need to ask you about it directly, my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look who we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... these are from my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He had too much to drink. Pretty unusual for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought him back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,First time it's happened, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't normally get like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this. Could you help me move him to the bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine... don't trouble yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine... just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, already, I'll go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to Germany alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, don't give up so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My dear brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, just come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like Henmi asked us to do this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:14:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't get the wrong idea about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to spend some more time with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've talked enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider his feelings some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have! I {\i1}have{\i0} thought about him! That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I did what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...I really don't understand all of this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kaoru-no-Kimi, I know that you need to be with my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More than anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you love him, and yet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The more she thinks of him, the more determined she becomes to leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just the way she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That just doesn't make any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people... suppose two people are in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the woman has a life threatening illness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman believes that she has only five years left to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she knew that, she broke up with the man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of the one she loved... for the sake of his future...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She felt that she couldn't risk ruining that future of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She felt that it would be best if they led their own separate lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She felt that she was doing it because she loved him so very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But is that love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really love?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:16:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Love isn't as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,, don't think that we can really know whether their love is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hope to find some sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,some proof that it's real; but you can never really know whether what you see is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why suffer? Why wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's waited for her for a whole year!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A year he has waited, and he still loves her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it still hurts him, he still suffers, and now he may be on the verge of giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He may end up going to Germany alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.84,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about Takehiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is Takehiko that we're talking about, that love is most likely genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.58,0:16:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what may come of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...if their love is true, then whatever happens will be for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It might not be too much longer before you fall in love with a boy yourself, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But that will be your love, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A unique thing, unlike anything that you have known before, a true love of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't the answer I was looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well anyway, it's time to shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So it was you. I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the one who has been ensuring that the flowers are always fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san, Arikura-san, Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.45,0:18:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Two or three girls from Rei's class, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They all came to change the flowers, each drawn here for her own reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here because I wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you will not be going to Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a personal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see any reason why I should have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Most likely, I would end up being nothing but a burden to him, able to give nothing in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years... no, I think that I have only four years left now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have four years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of Rei living life to its fullest, right down to the last minute, the last second!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have four years left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.45,0:20:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Live it with all your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,As Rei did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You have four years! In those four years, anything is possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, in one summer, in one week... you found the love of a lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,To even think that you would hold yourself back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not like you, Orihara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whiskey and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san here said that she just had to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oolong tea, please. I'm driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you! Please don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to Germany by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it! You can't! You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ever say that I would?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time, when you were drunk, back in you room...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I might have said something like that, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me borrow this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you feeling? What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I get depressed and lose my resolve for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I consider just throwing in the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But only for a moment. Only for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I really seem like such a pathetic guy as that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.46,0:22:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy so worthless,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he couldn't shoulder her pain, who wouldn't even concern himself with her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the kind of big brother I seem to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have finally come to understand just how painful it can be to love someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.42,0:22:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am beginning to realize just how wonderful a thing it can be, as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.53,0:23:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When the final day comes, I'll probably be crying out, I'll be so afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When the time comes, will you hold my hand? Hold me tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, if these hands of mine are good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.22,0:23:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course... after all... you're all I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:14.01,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:19.48,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:25.09,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.09,0:24:30.56,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.30,0:24:36.84,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.84,0:24:42.31,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.31,0:24:45.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.04,0:24:47.85,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.85,0:24:50.25,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.25,0:24:55.52,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.56,0:25:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In the next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.98,0:25:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of youth has come to an end for Nanako and her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.07,0:25:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru and Henmi have set off for Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.35,0:25:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.36,0:25:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...two years later, as springtime again draws near...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.91,0:25:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...Nanako receives a letter from Henmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.93,0:25:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The final chapter: A Lingering Fragrance
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.88,0:25:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear brother... there is no end to my tears...
